0.2.6 (03/08/2022)
------------------
- Revised 103: listing online devices. Added class 'OfflineDeviceInput' that only requires the keys that exist in the database for creating a device object. api._create_devices() uses this class for casting to, in case no extra keys are passed

0.2.7 (03/08/2022)
------------------
- Revised 103: added OfflineDeviceInput and OfflineDevice, and functions to check whether we should return one of those or not.

0.2.8 (03/08/2022)
------------------
- Revised 103: added 'OnlineDevice' as an intermediate state for creating quantum and simulator devices. Helps us get rid of some variables that we may have in creation, as the number of queued jobs, that only affect to devices that are online. Allows us to keep the base Device class as one where everything is required, with no if clauses in its __init__

0.2.9 (03/08/2022)
